Page_0: "Notice to all civilians:

The curfew for the Market District will remain in effect until further notice. Smegglers Shoppe will remain closed during the day, and the gates to the district will remain closed at night until the brigands responsible for looting this store are found. This curfew is for your own safety. Please respect the law and take care of all business you have in the district before nightfall.

-Sheriff Gorman Truart"